#: templates/base.html:9
msgid "ZLT Company Profile | Modern Farming Solutions"
msgstr "ZLT Company Profile | Kurima Kwechizvinozvino"

#: templates/base.html:10
msgid ""
"ZLT designs and builds farm infrastructure for Zimbabwe’s climate, soil, and "
"farmers. Land prep, irrigation, storage, agri-tech consulting."
msgstr ""
"ZLT inogadzira nekuvaka zvivakwa zvepurazi zvemamiriro ekunze eZimbabwe, ivhu, "
"nevarimi. Kugadzirira minda, kudiridza, kuchengetedza, mazano etekinoroji yekurima."

#: templates/base.html:11
msgid ""
"Zimbabwe farming, agricultural infrastructure, irrigation systems, farm "
"storage, ZLT, tobacco farming"
msgstr ""
"Kurima kweZimbabwe, zvivakwa zvekurima, masisitimu ekudiridza, kuchengetedza "
"kwepurazi, ZLT, kurima fodya"

