#: templates/base.html:88 templates/core/home.html:12
msgid "Zimbabwe Leaf Tobacco"
msgstr "Zimbabwe Leaf Tobacco"

#: templates/base.html:88
msgid "Built with pride by a ZLT team member."
msgstr "Yakagadzirwa nerudo nenhengo yechikwata cheZLT."

#: templates/core/about.html:4
msgid "About ZLT | Building Zimbabwe’s Tobacco Future"
msgstr "Nezve ZLT | Kuvaka Ramangwana reFodya reZimbabwe"

#: templates/core/about.html:5
msgid ""
"For over 60 years, ZLT has been the trusted partner for tobacco growers "
"nationwide. Fair markets, sustainable growth, and grower support."
msgstr ""
"Kwemakore anodarika 60, ZLT yanga iri shamwari yakavimbika yevarimi vefodya "
"munyika yese. Misika yakanaka, budiriro yakasimba, uye nekutsigira yevarimi."

#: templates/core/about.html:6
msgid "About Zimbabwe Leaf Tobacco"
msgstr "Nezve Zimbabwe Leaf Tobacco"

#: templates/core/about.html:7
msgid ""
"We build relationships with growers. From smallholder farmers to commercial "
"growers, ZLT provides infrastructure, transparency, and support."
msgstr ""
"Tinovaka hukama nevarimi. Kubva kuvarimi vadiki kusvika kuvarimi vakuru, "
"ZLT inopa zvivakwa, zvikwanisiro, uye tsigiro."

#: templates/core/about.html:13
msgid "Building Zimbabwe’s Tobacco Future"
msgstr "Kuvaka Ramangwana reFodya reZimbabwe"

#: templates/core/about.html:14
msgid ""
"For over 60 years, Zimbabwe Leaf Tobacco has been the trusted partner for "
"growers nationwide, delivering fair markets and sustainable growth."
msgstr ""
"Kwemakore anodarika 60, Zimbabwe Leaf Tobacco yanga iri shamwari yakavimbika "
"yevarimi munyika yese, ichiunza misika yakanaka nebudiriro yakasimba."

#: templates/core/about.html:15
msgid ""
"We don’t just run auctions. We build relationships. From smallholder farmers "
"in Marondera to commercial growers in Mashonaland, ZLT provides the "
"infrastructure, transparency, and support that turns harvest into income."
msgstr ""
"Hatingomhanyisa ma auction chete. Tinovaka hukama. Kubva kuvarimi vadiki "
"muMarondera kusvika kuvarimi vakuru kuMashonaland, ZLT inopa zvivakwa, "
"kujeka, uye tsigiro inoshandura goho kuita mari."

#: templates/core/about.html:19
msgid "Years of Service"
msgstr "Makore Ebasa"

#: templates/core/about.html:23
msgid "Auction Floors"
msgstr "Ma Auction Floors"

#: templates/core/about.html:27
msgid "Growers Supported"
msgstr "Varimi Vanotsigirwa"

#: templates/core/about.html:34
msgid "Our Commitment"
msgstr "Chitsidzo Chedu"

#: templates/core/about.html:36
msgid "Transparent pricing and payments"
msgstr "Mitengo nekubhadhara kuri pachena"

#: templates/core/about.html:37
msgid "Timely settlement within 72 hours"
msgstr "Kubhadhara nenguva mukati memaawa 72"

#: templates/core/about.html:38
msgid "Technical agronomy support"
msgstr "Tsigiro yehunyanzvi hwekurima"

#: templates/core/about.html:39
msgid "Access to inputs and financing"
msgstr "Kuwana zvekushandisa nemari"

#: templates/core/home.html:4
msgid "ZLT Home | Zimbabwe Leaf Tobacco"
msgstr "ZLT | Zimbabwe Leaf Tobacco"

#: templates/core/home.html:5
msgid ""
"ZLT supports tobacco growers with auction services, contract farming, and "
"grower support across Zimbabwe since 1964."
msgstr ""
"ZLT inotsigira varimi vefodya ne auction, kurima kwakabvumiranwa, uye "
"tsigiro yevarimi muZimbabwe yese kubva 1964."

#: templates/core/home.html:6
msgid "Zimbabwe Leaf Tobacco | ZLT"
msgstr "Zimbabwe Leaf Tobacco | ZLT"

#: templates/core/home.html:7 templates/core/home.html:13
msgid "Supporting growers. Delivering quality tobacco. Since 1964."
msgstr "Kutsigira varimi. Kuunza fodya yemhando yepamusoro. Kubva 1964."

#: templates/core/home.html:14
msgid "Get in Touch"
msgstr "Tibatei"

#: templates/core/home.html:23
msgid "Auction Services"
msgstr "Ma Auction"

#: templates/core/home.html:24
msgid ""
"Transparent and competitive tobacco sales across our auction floors "
"nationwide."
msgstr ""
"Kutengeswa kwefodya kuri pachena uye kune makwikwi mumafloors edu "
"munyika yese."

#: templates/core/home.html:31
msgid "Contract Farming"
msgstr "Kurima Kwakabvumiranwa"

#: templates/core/home.html:32
msgid ""
"Input support, agronomy advice, and guaranteed markets for our contracted "
"growers."
msgstr ""
"Tsigiro yezvekushandisa, mazano ekurima, uye misika yakavimbiswa "
"yevarimi vedu."

#: templates/core/home.html:39
msgid "Grower Support"
msgstr "Tsigiro Yevarimi"

#: templates/core/home.html:40
msgid ""
"Timely payments, training programs, and market information to help you "
"succeed."
msgstr ""
"Kubhadhara nenguva, zvirongwa zvekudzidzisa, uye ruzivo rwemusika "
"kuti ubudirire."
